---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="MyTempo Privacy Policy">
  <main id="main" class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pb-section pt-4 sm:px-8 sm:pt-6">
    <section class="fade-up space-y-6" style="animation-delay: 120ms">
      <h2 class="section-title">MyTempo Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-ink/90 sm:text-lg">
        Effective date: January 19, 2026
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink/90 sm:text-lg">
        
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Overview</h3>
          <p>
            MyTempo ("the App") is developed by Connor Forsythe. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains that the App does not collect, store, or share any of your personal information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Data Collection</h3>
          <p>
            We do not collect any personal data from our users. You do not need to create an account or log in to use MyTempo. We do not track your usage, location, or device identifiers, and we do not use third-party analytics services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">On-Device Data</h3>
          <p>
            Any data you create within the App (such as saved songs, setlists, or arrangements) is stored locally on your device. We do not have access to this data, and it is never uploaded to external servers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Third-Party Services</h3>
          <p>
            The App does not include any third-party SDKs, advertisements, or tracking tools.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Changes</h3>
          <p>
            We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. You are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Contact</h3>
          <p>
            If you have any questions or suggestions about this Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at 
            <a href="mailto:connorrforsythe@gmail.com" class="underline hover:text-ink/80">connorrforsythe@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
